WEBVTT

00:11.500 --> 00:13.500
(wind whistling)

00:27.800 --> 00:30.000
(indistinct announcement
over P. A.)

00:36.600 --> 00:39.400
(buzzing in distance)

00:51.733 --> 00:53.733
(thudding in distance)

01:02.333 --> 01:04.333
(metal creaking)

01:35.166 --> 01:37.166
(metal creaking)

02:06.166 --> 02:08.166
(chuckles)

02:30.633 --> 02:34.200
(both laugh)

02:34.233 --> 02:38.033
(both whooping)

02:38.066 --> 02:40.700
♪ You can't roller‐skate
in a buffalo herd ♪

02:40.733 --> 02:43.466
♪ You can't roller‐skate in
a buffalo herd ♪

02:43.500 --> 02:46.233
♪ You can't roller‐skate
in a buffalo herd ♪

02:46.266 --> 02:49.233
