49:57.233 --> 50:02.133
DOCTOR SENATOR:
You know, my father worked in
a slaughterhouse for 33 years.

50:02.166 --> 50:06.300
Yeah. Butchering cows
and pigs, chickens.

50:06.333 --> 50:10.800
All day long, he cut up
rib eye and, uh, lamb chops.

50:10.833 --> 50:13.166
Ribs.

50:13.200 --> 50:15.333
You know what we ate?

50:15.366 --> 50:17.700
Pigs' feet.

50:17.733 --> 50:20.233
Ham hocks, neck bones.

50:20.266 --> 50:21.566
Scraps.

50:21.600 --> 50:23.300
CALAMITA:
What did I tell you?

50:23.333 --> 50:25.166
They like to talk.

50:25.200 --> 50:27.500
See, in America,
even the food means something.

50:27.533 --> 50:30.200
Means whether you're up or down,
in or out.

50:30.233 --> 50:32.400
White, colored.

50:35.166 --> 50:37.466
This is ours.

50:37.500 --> 50:39.500
We haven't met.

50:41.833 --> 50:44.033
I'm Doctor Senator.

50:49.733 --> 50:52.600
You got to give respect
to get respect.

50:56.300 --> 50:59.766
Is that why you Americans
are so soft?

50:59.800 --> 51:02.333
All this giving and getting?

51:13.200 --> 51:16.733
In the land of taking
and killing, Gaetano is king.

51:16.766 --> 51:18.766
(bolt gun fires)

51:18.800 --> 51:21.166
Easy.

51:26.500 --> 51:29.633
A deal was made.

51:29.666 --> 51:32.166
On high.

51:32.200 --> 51:35.333
Wednesday, last.

51:35.366 --> 51:38.200
Oh.

51:38.233 --> 51:42.233
Well, this might be a news flash
for his majesty.

51:42.266 --> 51:44.233
Hmm.

51:44.266 --> 51:50.200
A deal between Fadda the senior

51:50.233 --> 51:52.666
and my man, Cannon.

51:54.700 --> 51:57.366
Mm‐hmm.
(chuckles)

51:57.400 --> 52:01.333
Territory was allotted

52:01.366 --> 52:06.200
from your organization
to the Negro syndicate.

52:06.233 --> 52:07.633
Given.

52:08.800 --> 52:13.466
Well, this is us,
come to collect.

52:13.500 --> 52:16.666
(chuckles)

52:16.700 --> 52:20.433
That sound like mulignan
bullshit to me.

52:20.466 --> 52:24.033
Am I talking to you or to him?

52:24.066 --> 52:26.466
(bolt gun fires)

52:26.500 --> 52:27.500
Easy.

52:48.400 --> 52:53.733
If you can't respect that,
then we can't respect anything.

52:53.766 --> 52:59.466
Very clever...
these words you hide behind.

53:03.433 --> 53:05.233
How do you think
your words will taste,

53:05.266 --> 53:09.000
spit from the mouth of the wolf?

53:10.400 --> 53:11.566
Hmm?

53:16.066 --> 53:19.600
Muscle and bone.
This is the power.

53:19.633 --> 53:21.166
Not all your...

53:35.466 --> 53:38.333
(exhales)

53:38.366 --> 53:42.033
If this is a misunderstanding,
let us see.

53:42.066 --> 53:44.033
You take your men, go home.

53:44.066 --> 53:49.200
I'll talk to my brother,
feel if this is what you say.

53:49.233 --> 53:51.233
And if so...

54:01.233 --> 54:03.233
But if no?

54:06.833 --> 54:09.033
DOCTOR SENATOR:
Happy's cousin.

54:09.066 --> 54:10.633
Easy, Happy's cousin.

54:25.133 --> 54:27.133
(bolt gun fires)

54:40.500 --> 54:42.500
Molto bene.

54:47.300 --> 54:51.700
But remember: we'll be back.

54:53.333 --> 54:57.666
Because y'all just got here
yesterday.

54:57.700 --> 55:00.533
But we're part of this land,

55:00.566 --> 55:04.500
like the wind and the dirt.

55:13.833 --> 55:17.333
LOY:
Lord, we know the road is long.

55:17.366 --> 55:20.333
We thank you for that road,

55:20.366 --> 55:22.566
because the journey
makes us wise.

55:22.600 --> 55:24.766
We know the climb is hard.

55:24.800 --> 55:28.766
We thank you for that climb,
'cause climbing makes us strong.

55:28.800 --> 55:30.000
Amen.

55:32.100 --> 55:35.200
LOY:
You made the land and the sea,

55:35.233 --> 55:38.066
and you filled it
with injustice

55:38.100 --> 55:41.033
so that we would have
work to do.

55:41.066 --> 55:43.700
And we thank you for that work.

55:49.100 --> 55:53.600
You made the meek, so the meek
could inherit the Earth.

55:53.633 --> 55:57.500
And you made the mighty so that
we could defend the meek.

56:04.166 --> 56:06.033
Let us pray.

56:06.066 --> 56:10.266
LOY:
And we will be mighty
for you, O Lord.

56:10.300 --> 56:12.133
You've shown us
pain and loss...

56:12.166 --> 56:14.300
(laughter)

56:14.333 --> 56:17.000
...so that we would know the
joy of victory when it comes.

56:22.200 --> 56:24.200
♪ ♪

56:53.566 --> 56:56.233
LOY:
Hear our prayer now, O Lord...

56:58.366 --> 57:01.100
...so that we might feel
your blessing.

57:03.400 --> 57:08.533
And know that we can bear
this burden you've given us

57:08.566 --> 57:12.500
because our hearts are pure.

57:12.533 --> 57:15.066
‐Amen.
‐OTHERS: Amen.

